name: Eddie Halliwell
description: '''Eddie Halliwell''' (born  1979 or 1980) is an English [[electronic dance music]] disc jockey who plays [[techno]], [[house music|house]] and [[trance music|trance]] music. Known for his live performances he has regularly featured in the [[DJ Mag]] top 100 DJ list, and has performed several times on the [[BBC Radio 1]] [[Essential Mix]] show.
